recommendation.text: My husband and I are completely ignorant in the field of gardening, Yossi from the nursery guided us patiently until we reached the desired result that is both beautiful and suitable for our needs and of course for the cold climate of Jerusalem,highly recommend

I asked for a recommendation for durable and colorful perennial seedlings, So that I do not have to replace the seedlings in the garden every year. Since my garden is northern and without sunshine, I was directed straight into the realm of begonias,Very pleased with the result!!!

The recommendation for 'Queen of the Night'and Jasmine was accurate, the smell of honey wafting from a distance is insane ..., what's more it is a durable plant that does not need much work and investment.Thank you to the site staff for the amazing service
A wide variety of shrubs that are not seen anywhere, Answer me politely for any question, I got a lot of helpful advice...;)
Nowhere have I seen such a wide variety of succulents,Your gardener advised me and directed me, For a perfect garden just like I wanted with a minimum of effort

I was amazed at the beautiful colors of the seasonal plants,  I was debating what is suitable for a garden that does not have much sun in the winter, the nursery staff helped me make the right decisions,and all this without leaving home !!!
